	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hodie synodus nostra, reverende in Christo pater, solita est, quae iam duravit triduum totum.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Causa <persName type="auto_name">Leonis</persName> recruduerat et nos detinuit plures horas; post longam demum concertationem haec ab illo extorsimus, quae mitto.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quae omnia tibi prolixius charissimus noster frater d. <persName type="auto_name">Huldrychus Campellus</persName>, si petieris, pro candore suo exponere poterit, ex quo et audies, quis causam d. <persName type="auto_name">Leonis</persName> egerit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Plura proxime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De concilio quae sciri potuerunt, ex d. <persName type="auto_name">Iulio</persName> intellexisti.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribit d. Traversius et promittit d. <persName ref="p17927" cert="high">Friderychus</persName> se posthac certa habituros; sibi enim esse consanguineum, qui versetur in aula ducis <placeName type="auto_name">Mantuani</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Die krönung <persName ref="p18556" cert="high">Maximiliani</persName> (die behömisch krönung) ist wider abgeschaffen; <foreign xml:lang="la">est certum.</foreign></s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Es hat sich der graaff von <placeName type="auto_name">Sultz</placeName> und andere ouch schon daruff gerüst, und als sy diser tagen habend verryten wöllen, ist uff der post die sach abkündt; <foreign xml:lang="la">causam ignoro.</foreign></s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="de"><placeName type="auto_name">Sfortia</placeName> sol von den Venedigern gefangen,</foreign> alii putant sublatum; dicitur indignius tractasse nescio quem magnum Venetum.<note type="misc">gestrichen.</note></s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed omnia proxime prolixius; haec nunc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Certe adeo defectus sum concionando (sed nondum finis), ut non possim amplius.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ignosce et de rebus <persName type="auto_name">Gallicis</persName> nos edoce; nam omnes anxie expectamus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale d. d. pater.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curię</placeName> 29. maii anno 1562.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tui observantissimus <persName ref="p8009" cert="high">Ioan[nes] F[abricius]</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Has literas pridie scripsi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc ita subito discedunt, ut plura non possim; sed scribam cras et puto ex nostris profecturos.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Transiit hac quidam <persName type="auto_name">Tridentinus</persName> per postam, qui videtur explorator nec negare potest marchionem de <persName type="auto_name">Peschier</persName> domum rediisse; alii autem pro certo affirmant (sed ego nihil affirmo) marchionem, qui illuc missus erat nomine <persName type="auto_name">Philippi</persName> regis, protestatum cum episcopis non procedendum, dum pontifex se subiiciat concilio.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Plura nunc non possum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Amplissimo viro eruditione et pietate singulari d. Heinrycho Bullingero, ecclesiae Tigurinae antistiti vigilantissimo, domino et patrono suo etc.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
